<font class="post">
... Logging from Combat is seriously messed up.<br><br>While I (naturally) have an account I simply haven't had time to check things out yet but a friend (BOUND4DOOM from server 103) tells me that the ability to log from a critter has been removed.<br><br>Hopefully this will apply to PvP as well.<br><br>If so... Folks reading this might wanna consider checking it out.<br><br>If not.. Avoid it like the plague.<br><br>Artfully Yours,<br><br>Nnuk (aKa Canuck from 103)<br>Artist of Death<br><a href="http://www.artfuldeath.com" target="_blank">www.artfuldeath.com</a><br><a href="http://www.tusrz.com" target="_blank">www.tusrz.com</a>  


