<td width="83%" class="lighttable">
<br />
<font class="post">
That was 3DO's "solution" to Alt-F4 and I remember when I was asked into the beta that introduced this all too well.<br><br>I'd just spent the previous 3+ months banging my head against the wall trying to get the ability to Log from Combat removed from the game (it had always been possible to do so but it wasn't a problem until everyone started doing it) and I was asked to come test out the fix.<br><br>Despite my constant harping on the subject they never did correct the problem... That was actually what made me move everyone I knew to EQ -- Verant's method of keeping folks from pulling the plug at the first sign of danger was <i>precisely</i> what I'd been begging 3DO for.<br><br>Artfully Yours,<br><br>Nnuk<br>Artist of Death &amp; Member of <a href="http://www.tusrz.com" target="_blank">T.U.S.</a><br><a href="http://www.artfuldeath.com" target="_blank">Artful Death Gallery</a>  


